    "created_at": "2015-07-19T08:16:20Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-07-19T08:16:20Z",
    "body": "> The BrowserWindow's unmaximize and maximize functions appear to have a side-effect: hidden windows will suddenly be shown. \n\nThe `maximize` and `minimize` API behavior(a hidden window will be showed after the API called) here is expected, see #834. But after test,  the behavior is not consistent on three platforms, only work on Windows.\n"
